cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.AI 

This paper deals with video retargeting, which involves manipulating the content and style of videos. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also uses adversarial losses, which are commonly used in generative models and fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) category. Additionally, the paper deals with spatiotemporal information, which is relevant to graphics (cs.GR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories.
